flowchart TD
    %% Logical schema generated from Lima & Mello 2015 rules
    %% Main comparison mode: SchemaLens-consistent cardinality evidence

    Corporation["Collection: Corporation"]
    Industry["Embedded: Industry"]
    Country["Embedded: Country"]
    FinancialReport["Embedded/Collection: FinancialReport"]
    ListedSecurity["Collection: ListedSecurity"]
    CorporationRef["Reference: Corporation"]

    Person["Collection: Person"]
    FinancialServiceAccount["Embedded/Collection: FinancialServiceAccount"]
    Holding["Embedded/Collection: Holding"]

    Transaction["Collection: Transaction"]
    BuyTransaction["Folded into Transaction: BuyTransaction"]
    SellTransaction["Specialization: SellTransaction"]

    ReportElement["Embedded/Collection: ReportElement"]
    StatementElement["Reference: StatementElement"]
    Disclosure["Reference: Disclosure"]
    Security["Reference: Security"]

    %% Corporation-centered decisions
    Corporation -->|RULE_5 descriptor: corporation_has_industry| Industry
    Corporation -->|RULE_5 descriptor: corporation_has_country| Country
    Corporation -->|RULE_5 containment: corporation_has_financial_report| FinancialReport
    ListedSecurity -.->|RULE_6 reference: corporation_has_listed_security| CorporationRef

    %% Reporting decisions
    FinancialReport -->|RULE_5 containment: financial_report_contains_report_element| ReportElement
    FinancialReport -.->|RULE_6 reference: financial_report_contains_disclosure| Disclosure
    ReportElement -.->|RULE_6 reference: report_element_has_statement_element| StatementElement

    %% Person/account/holding decisions
    Person -->|RULE_5 ownership: person_owns_financial_service_account| FinancialServiceAccount
    FinancialServiceAccount -->|RULE_5 containment: account_has_holding| Holding
    FinancialServiceAccount -->|RULE_5 containment: account_records_transaction| Transaction

    %% Security/transaction decisions
    Transaction -->|RULE_5 association: transaction_refers_to_listed_security| ListedSecurity
    ListedSecurity -->|RULE_5 association: holding_refers_to_listed_security| Holding
    ListedSecurity -.->|RULE_6 reference: listed_security_represents_security| Security

    %% Generalization decisions
    Transaction -->|RULE_1 fold subclass| BuyTransaction
    Transaction -->|RULE_3 preserve specialization| SellTransaction
